      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PROJECT NEMESIS (2) showed strong early pace and proved too slick around this track over 400m in 22.97, claiming a Maiden by 9 lengths. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Looks the testing material. HOOKED ON HOPE (4) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at Gosford over 388m behind Imogene Pass (22.92) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Better than last start and can bounce back. CHUTZPAH (1) clocked a new course and distance PB last time, finishing a 3.5 lengths second behind Bumpy Blue in 23.08. Expected to feature again. DOLLAR ROLEX (3) was in the money again last time and not beaten far when second (22.48) at Gosford in a Grade 5.",
